pros:
I worked as seasonal part-time specialist and while it was hard to manage 2 jobs (I had a full time at the moment too), my team at Apple still made it an unforgettable experience! It's amazing how diverse and inclusive the company is. Being from a different country I felt very welcoming and understood. 
Some of the pros: 
- competitive hourly pay;
- flexible hours; 
- employee discount;
- fun and very positive environment!
